{"_path":"/zh_hans/getting-started/sceneobject/prototype","_dir":"sceneobject","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"场景对象原型","description":"场景对象原型是预先定义的一类对象，由公共模块以及预安装的场景对象模块组成。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"场景对象原型是预先定义的一类对象，由"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公共模块"}]},{"type":"text","value":"以及"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"预安装的场景对象模块"}]},{"type":"text","value":"组成。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每个场景对象都有它的原型，原型拥有的特性，该对象就拥有。（比如小明的原型是人类，而旺财的原型是狗）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高级开发人员可编辑原型，详细资料请参考自定义编辑器-场景对象原型。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"比如定义了人类和动物两种原型，他们都拥有移动速度这种属性。我们把所有物种共同的特性都放在公共模块中实现"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:zh_hans:getting-started:8.sceneobject:2.prototype.md","_source":"content","_file":"zh_hans/getting-started/8.sceneobject/2.prototype.md","_stem":"zh_hans/getting-started/8.sceneobject/2.prototype","_extension":"md"}